metadata.name: TTTreasures #1
metadata.description: A Collection of Genesis Gems living on the Ethereum Blockchain. TTTreasures is a Singapore based community-driven NFT project aiming to be the bridging point for web 3.0 and in real life conventions where like minded people seek endless opportunities for growth and excellence. Holding a Gem gives you voting rights to our TTTreasury and grants access to members-only benefits IRL and in web 3.0.
